user.canProvide: Happy to help anyone practice / learn Spanish or offer recommendations when visiting South America. I also know a little too much about the design of a Newton's Cradle — feel free to ask me about the massive Newton's Cradle I built.
user.currentRole: Student at Wisconsin School of Business | Venture Partner at Contrary
user.intro:
Hello — My name is Dylan Hart, a third-year student and VP at Wisconsin. I was born in NY and spent time growing up with my side of the family in Argentina (Buenos Aries).  

I am interested in fintech, CRISPR, football, freelance industry, and AI — always happy to find a time and chat!
user.lookingFor: I am looking to collaborate with anyone building for the gig economy or thinking about changing how people do independent work.
